CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1965, pg. 7 reads: "Man Of Year" - One of the highlights of the Rose Ball given by Alpha Omicron Lambda Chapter of Alpha Phi Alpha Fraternity, last Friday night at Hotel Webster Hall, was naming Mal Goode the chapter's "Man of the Year." Left to right: The Rev. LeRoy Patrick, who presented the citation to the ABC-TV newsman; Goode and Dr. Woody Harris, president of the Alpha Chapter. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Two men and two women wearing formal wear, seated around circular banquet table with Coca Cola bottles and cameras, in Webster Hall for Alpha Phi Alpha Rose Ball
